                        </persName>, their manor of <placeName type="manor" key="place_102008">Otham</placeName> for 20 years, paying to the <orgName key="org_102002">abbot and convent of Begham</orgName> five marks sterling, and to the <orgName key="org_102015">prior and convent of Michelham</orgName> 25 marks annually. 
